Class UnreliableStack<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.ReliableStack<T>
      • models.UnreliableStack<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasInvariant, UnboundedStorageSpecification<T>

    public class UnreliableStack<T>
extends ReliableStack<T>
    This class is an extension of ReliableStack
    It overrides push(), pop() and head() and adds the exception condition to make Stack to be unreliable
    Author:
    btdiem
